high_descs: Turn left and move ahead towards the coffeetable in the living room.
Pick up the eggplant from the center table in the living room.
Take the fruit and walk away straight towards the kitchen sink.
Put the eggplant in the kitchen sink.
Go left, walk, take right and enter the bedroom nearby the eggplant table.
Pick a second eggplant from the bedroom table.
Take the second fruit, walk away and turn left towards the kitchen sink.
Put the eggplant in the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Collect two eggplants from bedroom, living room and put it in the kitchen SinkBasin.

high_descs: Turn right. Go forward. When you reach the shelf, turn left. Exit and then turn right. After the exit, turn right. When you enter the room, turn left. When you get near the coffeetable, turn right.
Grab the eggplant.
Turn right. Continue forward and turn right at the gate. Before reaching the shelf, turn right. When you reach the sink, turn right.
Place the eggplant in the sink on the left side next to the pot.
Turn right. Move forward. When you reach the eggplant, turn left. At the end of the wall, turn right. Turn right to be in front of the nightstand.
Grab the eggplant.
Turn right. When leaving the room, turn left. When you reach the shelf, turn right. When you reach the sink, turn right.
Place the eggplant over the sink.
anns.task_desc: Search for two eggplants. Place them in a SinkBasin.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the coffeetable near the couch.
Take the eggplant from the table.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the eggplant into the sink.
Turn around and go to the eggplant.
Take another eggplant from the side table.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the eggplant into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Collect the Eggplant and placed it into the SinkBasin.
